25:06.570 --> 25:09.038
- Let's see--
- Hey, what's in there?

25:09.070 --> 25:11.300
This is the snapper here--
no, I'll take this big one
right here.

25:11.340 --> 25:13.672
This one?

25:13.710 --> 25:15.268
- Yeah, that's perfect.
Thank you so much.
- Okay.

25:15.310 --> 25:18.279
What do we got in here?

25:18.310 --> 25:20.005
So, this is--
this is redfish
right here?

25:20.050 --> 25:21.677
- Yes.
- Yeah, that looks
really good.

25:21.720 --> 25:23.210
Let me see, you got--

25:23.250 --> 25:24.786
- Yeah, give me all of that.
- ( loud thumping )

25:24.820 --> 25:25.787
