How's Aunt Vi
holding up?

27:01.150 --> 27:04.119
She gonna be all right.

27:04.150 --> 27:07.711
Been through worse
and came out
on the other side.

27:07.760 --> 27:11.127
I ain't seen her
like this since
Ralph Angel's trial.

27:11.160 --> 27:14.129
That woman loves hard.

27:14.160 --> 27:18.699
- Hard for her
to let things go.
- ( truck beeping )

27:18.730 --> 27:20.391
Who is that?

27:20.430 --> 27:22.398
Whole bunch of peckerwoods.

27:26.310 --> 27:28.278
What the hell y'all think
y'all doin'?

27:28.310 --> 27:30.744
We're your servers.
