coming With us?

36:05.990 --> 36:08.925
Look, I respect ya,

36:08.960 --> 36:11.963
and I appreciate everything
you do for us.

36:12.000 --> 36:15.697
But he's mine, all right?

36:15.740 --> 36:18.208
I don't want him
seeing no coffin,

36:18.240 --> 36:21.232
