all the coddling he did
With you.

36:34.390 --> 36:36.585
His only son,
up on a pedestal.

36:36.620 --> 36:39.783
It ain't right,
it ain't healthy.

36:39.830 --> 36:42.390
See how it turns out.

36:45.330 --> 36:49.232
Oh, yeah?
How's that? Hmm?

36:49.270 --> 36:52.307
Wrestling with the world.

36:52.340 --> 36:55.275
