38:25.570 --> 38:28.733
Wait. Charley, wait.

38:30.040 --> 38:31.837
Charley.

38:34.440 --> 38:37.079
Baby-- okay,
you were right.

38:37.110 --> 38:39.101
Everything's not
about me, okay?

38:39.150 --> 38:40.970
